messages.content: You're going to have to give me an address or a street marker.
Just stay with me. I don't know the address.
Okay. Can you tell me anything that's around you? Try to think.
Behind Cal-Safe? How far behind Cal-Safe?
That's the number. 627, is it Sunrise Park or Cherry Street or away?
Listen to me, I'm going to get somebody on the way, but just tell me what happened.
Oh, no. They just went in there to get the... It was an accident. He shot them both.
Okay. So there are two people who have been shot?
All right. Just stay with me. You're there on Sunrise Park behind Cal-Safe. Where are they shot?
Oh, God. Just get down here. I don't know where they got shot. I don't want to move them.
Okay, stay with me. I've got the police department on the way, and I'm getting an ambulance on the way. What color is the house or trailer you're at?
It's a trailer? Okay. Are you on Love Avenue?
Okay. Are there several trailers around you?
I've got them on the way. I'm going to talk to you until they get there, so don't hang up. What is your name?
All right. And you're at 627 Sunrise Park?
Okay. Stay right where you are and I'm going to talk to you until an officer gets there.
So they went in there to get some papers?
Oh, shit. We shouldn't have gone in.
They went in, and he just came in there and shot them both.
He just left. He just booked it.
Did he leave on foot or in a car?
I don't know. I'm checking right now. Oh God, I can't see.
Okay. The police are here now.
Good. Talk to the officer. The subject involved has left the area, trying to ascertain if it was by vehicle or on foot. Are you still there?
Are you on foot or driving?
Okay. Just talk to me until you get to the residence and then we'll hang up, okay?
No, just them two, but I think they're dead.
Okay. And you said it was Matthew Moore?
Did you see him shoot them?
You need to tell the officers all this when they talk to you. Do you have any idea where he may have gone?
All right. Can you tell me if he left on foot or in a vehicle?
Do you know what kind of vehicle?
Okay. I'm going to hang up with you now, okay?
